{"tid":683514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返PT鍾意左個女仔","createTime":"2018-05-29T18:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T14:43:36.000Z","uid":39708,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff582f05d2c1f5786e93fa6159fd4de106ea1556","tid":683514,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇試過返工對同事心動<br />\n<br />\n嗰種感覺係無論份工幾垃圾都好<br />\n<br />\n只要鍾意嘅對象喺度<br />\n<br />\n你都會好想返<br />\n<br />\n如果嗰日佢冇返 <br />\n<br />\n你就會覺得嗰日好漫長<br />\n<br />\n你會掛住佢<br />\n<br />\n你會心不在焉<br />\n<br />\n喺佢面前<br />\n<br />\n你會想表現自己<br />\n<br />\n希望搏到佢注意<br />\n<br />\n見到佢同D異性同事傾計講笑<br />\n<br />\n你會妒忌人地有咁多機會同佢相處<br />\n<br />\n呢份工雖然辛苦，錢又唔多<br />\n<br />\n但因為你對佢心動，你唔會介意呢D野<br />\n<br />\n淨係想同佢有多D見面相處嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c84684b43edc499a3a843be7150386b827a3c2","tid":683514,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e89d463bbef0c2c4e986a28f12d1b23f0977cb8","tid":683514,"uid":156326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"咪撚咁毒啦"},{"pid":"e43b3b104d025a3505eda867bd2393ffe8b540b6","tid":683514,"uid":143173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"曾經試過 而且好鍾意<br />\n明知冇機 明知佢只係玩玩下撩女仔<br />\n差唔多日日見又見足八粒鐘<br />\n真係好辛苦<br />\n利申：已放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a7a20b1fd329590760ce7136dd7e1e42c7e93e","tid":683514,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上啊巴打"},{"pid":"dc19f10a0c44664af483953bf9fe54b9657f2aa4","tid":683514,"uid":102609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T19:55:13.000Z","msg":"我會同自己講<br />\n呢個只係太耐冇女而造成嘅錯覺<br />\n始終邊有咁多一見鐘情<br />\n然後過多排就會冇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e186338b988c0627c7bde9d92851f95bd6b04fd9","tid":683514,"uid":167721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"#2唔見左右<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1fe9902d255662f591b6fb0cdd2bb75763556e","tid":683514,"uid":156375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T20:09:42.000Z","msg":"我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為呢個原因係到捱左成年<br />\n份工幾遠都好都照返<br />\n但我就lastday lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攰啦都"},{"pid":"ad66193659236e13999c67ed5a8d6b17b33fbb78","tid":683514,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"都係放棄算<br />\n<br />\n淨係夠膽攞contact <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔夠膽約佢出街"},{"pid":"d4debb032645cd9506fbbbd1eb6e3ef2b09b9105","tid":683514,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad66193659236e13999c67ed5a8d6b17b33fbb78","tid":683514,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"都係放棄算<br />\n<br />\n淨係夠膽攞contact <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔夠膽約佢出街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"咁攞完有無傾計"},{"pid":"819caeb61698c7061024161a0c61b88d53d7401d","tid":683514,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4debb032645cd9506fbbbd1eb6e3ef2b09b9105","tid":683514,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad66193659236e13999c67ed5a8d6b17b33fbb78","tid":683514,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"都係放棄算<br 